    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative vehicle, maintained in pristine, showroom-ready condition. This motorcar exemplifies automotive excellence, having been preserved to an uncompromising standard that satisfies the most discerning collector. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously curated interior, reflects a legacy of absolute care. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a definitive example of the model, offering a driving experience that remains indistinguishable from its original delivery.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
